001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;
002
003import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.BaseSubProjectionNode;
004import java.lang.String;
005import java.util.ArrayList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008public class CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>, ROOT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>> extends BaseSubProjectionNode<PARENT, ROOT> {
009  public CustomFieldsTypeProjection(PARENT parent, ROOT root) {
010    super(parent, root, java.util.Optional.of("CustomFieldsType"));
011  }
012
013  public ReferenceProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> typeRef() {
014     ReferenceProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new ReferenceProjection<>(this, getRoot());
015     getFields().put("typeRef", projection);
016     return projection;
017  }
018
019  public TypeDefinitionProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> type() {
020     TypeDefinitionProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new TypeDefinitionProjection<>(this, getRoot());
021     getFields().put("type", projection);
022     return projection;
023  }
024
025  public RawCustomFieldProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> customFieldsRaw(
026      ) {
027     RawCustomFieldProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new RawCustomFieldProjection<>(this, getRoot());
028     getFields().put("customFieldsRaw", projection);
029     return projection;
030  }
031
032  public RawCustomFieldProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> customFieldsRaw(
033      List<String> includeNames, List<String> excludeNames) {
034    RawCustomFieldProjection<CustomFieldsTypeProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new RawCustomFieldProjection<>(this, getRoot());    
035    getFields().put("customFieldsRaw", projection);
036    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("customFieldsRaw", k -> new ArrayList<>());                      
037    InputArgument includeNamesArg = new InputArgument("includeNames", includeNames);
038    getInputArguments().get("customFieldsRaw").add(includeNamesArg);
039    InputArgument excludeNamesArg = new InputArgument("excludeNames", excludeNames);
040    getInputArguments().get("customFieldsRaw").add(excludeNamesArg);
041    return projection;
042  }
043}
